title: Add the location -23,69 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0xaaadc5ecd1ae5d9a67d625c0021d9a59e01b3a89 (Degen)

## Rare Pepe Gallery

![Rare Pepe Gallery](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/-23/69/map.png)

Should the scene located at -23,69 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

The scene located at -23,69 is the "Rare Pepe Gallery."

It showcases a curated selection of Rare Pepe Wallet NFTs, minted from 2016-18 on Counterparty. These XCP assets are wrapped in Emblem vaults for display in DCL.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/proposal/?id=d10e84b0-e1b2-11eb-a20f-d75df7f87ed8)**
